commit.message:
Use reject zones more for Palm Rejection (#122)

* Reject fingers in zone always, except when moving finger out of zone

* Clean up, remove data_pkt from RMI_2D_Sensor

* Use x delta for fingers in palm rej zones to see if their valid

* Remove mid_x from last commit

* Only invalidate fingers which are currently active

* Update configuration options
